name: standing_sex pov concept
description:
My data set for this was very small, so lots of repeats. You need to use it at lower strengths or it burns the image alot.

But. At lower strengths it does a pretty good job. Really low. Like 0.4 low for good results.

Trained on:

  • standing sex: standing sex

  • legs together: legs together

  • legs apart: legs slightly parted

  • imminent: slight penetration with whole penis visible

  • penetration: full penetration, penis still visible

  • ballsdeep: deep penetration, penis not visible

from above and foreshortening help, also works well with public and exhibitionism.

I might retrain. The first version works, but it's kinda hard to control for some of the more specific poses.

For example. legs together, and legs apart, you need to put attention on the together or the apart, but not legs. ie legs (together) or legs (apart)

For imminent, penetration, and ballsdeep? They work... ish, if you generate at 768x768, but for some reason don't seem to work at 512x768, and 512x768 has much better results overall? So not sure what to do about that.
